OL,3,CCalls for wider training in Jersey to
OL,4,Creduce ADHD waiting lists
OL,6,FA Scrutiny Panel in Jersey has found
OL,7,Fthat islanders with attention deficit
OL,8,Fhyperactivity disorder (ADHD) could
OL,9,Fexperience less stress, if more health
OL,10,Fstaff were trained to issue medication
OL,11,Fprescribed to manage the neurological
OL,12,Fcondition.
OL,14,FThe Health and Social Security
OL,15,FScrutiny Panel published a report
OL,16,Ffollowing its review of the current
OL,17,Fprocess for prescribing medication to
OL,18,Fadults with ADHD.
