OL,3,CCalls for wider training in Jersey to
OL,4,Creduce ADHD waiting lists
OL,6,FThe review began in July after the
OL,7,FPanel heard that ADHD medication can
OL,8,Fcurrently only be prescribed by a
OL,9,Fspecialist consultant psychiatrist,
OL,10,Frather than GPs and other trained
OL,11,Fstaff.
OL,13,FCurrently Jersey only has one in post
OL,14,Fwho can assess and diagnose patients,
OL,15,Fbut the Panel heard they spend the
OL,16,Fmajority of their time issuing repeat
OL,17,Fprescriptions.
OL,19,FAdults in Jersey are waiting around
OL,20,F3.5 years for an assessment at the
OL,21,Fmoment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
