OL,3,CCalls for wider training in Jersey to
OL,4,Creduce ADHD waiting lists
OL,6,FFollowing the report, the Panel is
OL,7,Fcalling for the Minister for Health
OL,8,Fand Social Services, Deputy Tom Binet,
OL,9,Fto introduce a training programme for
OL,10,Fnurses to allow them to give adults
OL,11,FADHD assessments as well.
OL,13,FThe Panel is asking for this programme
OL,14,Fto be implemented within the next
OL,15,Fthree months.
