OL,3,CCalls for wider training in Jersey to
OL,4,Creduce ADHD waiting lists
OL,6,FDeputy Louise Doublet, Chair of the
OL,7,FHealth and Social Security Scrutiny
OL,8,FPanel, said: "It is clear to the Panel
OL,9,Fthat people who have shared their
OL,10,Fexperiences with us feel let down by
OL,11,Fthe current system. They are
OL,12,Ffrustrated with the long wait for a
OL,13,Fdiagnosis and lack of communication
OL,14,Fregarding not only that, but the
OL,15,Fimpact the global shortage of ADHD
OL,16,Fmedication could have on them.
OL,18,F"While there is little that Jersey can
OL,19,Fdo to improve the situation regarding
OL,20,Fthe shortage, we can remove some of
OL,21,FtheJother obstacles people are facing.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
