OL,3,CCalls for wider training in Jersey to
OL,4,Creduce ADHD waiting lists
OL,6,F"Allowing more staff to issue repeat
OL,7,Fprescriptions is vital to this and is
OL,8,Fsomething that can be delivered within
OL,9,Fthe resources the department has and
OL,10,Fwithin a reasonable amount of time and
OL,11,Fwould dramatically improve people's
OL,12,Fexperiences.
OL,14,F"It would also give the Minister time
OL,15,Fto work with the Primary Care Board on
OL,16,Fthe proposed Shared Care Pathway,
OL,17,Fwhich would allow GPs to prescribe
OL,18,FADHD medication, and investigate what
OL,19,Fother options there are for other
